              "Help": "This flag needs to be set if you want to create a polyphonic version of your  C++ node to be used in a polyphonic context.\n\n> If you want to use this flag, the `IsPolyphonic` flag also needs to be set obviously.\n\nYou can deactivate this flag to reduce the compile time & binary size a little bit as it will skip the creation of the polyphonic class template.\n\n",
